[
    {
        "text": "And I tried hard to be proud of my service but all I could feel was shame.",
        "startTime": 1313,
        "endTime": 5789,
        "slowStartTime": 2120,
        "slowEndTime": 8909
    },
    {
        "text": "And racism could no longer mask the reality of the occupation.",
        "startTime": 6493,
        "endTime": 9325,
        "slowStartTime": 9889,
        "slowEndTime": 14212
    },
    {
        "text": "These were people.",
        "startTime": 9437,
        "endTime": 10197,
        "slowStartTime": 14305,
        "slowEndTime": 15521
    },
    {
        "text": "These were human beings.",
        "startTime": 10462,
        "endTime": 11681,
        "slowStartTime": 15843,
        "slowEndTime": 17746
    },
    {
        "text": "I've since been plagued by guilt anytime I see an elderly man,...",
        "startTime": 12069,
        "endTime": 15013,
        "slowStartTime": 18253,
        "slowEndTime": 22745
    },
    {
        "text": "...like the one who couldn't walk, who we rolled onto a stretcher,...",
        "startTime": 15307,
        "endTime": 18272,
        "slowStartTime": 23110,
        "slowEndTime": 27633
    },
    {
        "text": "...and told the Iraqi police to take him away.",
        "startTime": 18417,
        "endTime": 20217,
        "slowStartTime": 27775,
        "slowEndTime": 30550
    },
    {
        "text": "I feel guilt anytime I see a mother with her children,...",
        "startTime": 20721,
        "endTime": 22941,
        "slowStartTime": 31232,
        "slowEndTime": 34636
    },
    {
        "text": "...like the one who cried hysterically and screamed that we were worse than Saddam...",
        "startTime": 23346,
        "endTime": 26777,
        "slowStartTime": 35169,
        "slowEndTime": 40391
    },
    {
        "text": "...as we forced her from her home.",
        "startTime": 26880,
        "endTime": 28169,
        "slowStartTime": 40470,
        "slowEndTime": 42479
    },
    {
        "text": "I feel guilt anytime I see a young girl...",
        "startTime": 28813,
        "endTime": 30840,
        "slowStartTime": 43370,
        "slowEndTime": 46485
    },
    {
        "text": "...like the one I grabbed by the arm and dragged into the street.",
        "startTime": 31579,
        "endTime": 34526,
        "slowStartTime": 47518,
        "slowEndTime": 52014
    },
    {
        "text": "We were told we were fighting terrorists,...",
        "startTime": 35783,
        "endTime": 37479,
        "slowStartTime": 53824,
        "slowEndTime": 56444
    },
    {
        "text": "...but the real terrorist was me and the real terrorism is this occupation.",
        "startTime": 38213,
        "endTime": 41868,
        "slowStartTime": 57469,
        "slowEndTime": 63027
    },
    {
        "text": "Racism within the military has long been an important tool...",
        "startTime": 43135,
        "endTime": 46122,
        "slowStartTime": 64852,
        "slowEndTime": 69408
    },
    {
        "text": "...to justify the destruction and occupation of another country.",
        "startTime": 46215,
        "endTime": 49166,
        "slowStartTime": 69473,
        "slowEndTime": 73974
    },
    {
        "text": "It has long been used to justify the killing, subjugation and torture of another people.",
        "startTime": 49603,
        "endTime": 53820,
        "slowStartTime": 74554,
        "slowEndTime": 80955
    },
    {
        "text": "Racism is a vital weapon employed by this government.",
        "startTime": 54391,
        "endTime": 57158,
        "slowStartTime": 81737,
        "slowEndTime": 85962
    },
    {
        "text": "It is a more important weapon than a rifle, a tank, a bomber or a battleship.",
        "startTime": 57681,
        "endTime": 62296,
        "slowStartTime": 86671,
        "slowEndTime": 93669
    },
    {
        "text": "It is more destructive than an artillery shell or a bunker buster or a Tomahawk missile.",
        "startTime": 62543,
        "endTime": 67613,
        "slowStartTime": 93965,
        "slowEndTime": 101645
    }
]